        "name": "Lift Nature's Caul",
        "desc": "You have seen the world around you as if a gauzy film had been lifted away to expose the truth that lies below your perceived reality. Natural features have grown twisted and horrendous, structures appeared distorted and ruined, and objects seemed warped and alien. The vision has faded quickly, but the glimpse beyond the natural world lingers for the spell's duration.\n\nUnless you are an aberration or worshipper of Outer Gods or Great Old Ones, you are negatively affected according to your Will saving throw.\n\n<strong>Critical Success</strong> You are unaffected and temporarily immune for 1 hour.\n<strong>Success</strong> You are sickened 1.\n<strong>Failure</strong> You are stupefied 1 for <var>var1</var> and frightened 1.\n<strong>Critical Failure</strong> You are stupefied 1 for <var>var1</var> and frightened 2. You can't reduce the value of your frightened condition below 1 as long as you remain stupefied by this spell.",
